    "title": [
      "[Shanty Town, The Garden]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Faded gravel pathways create a series of meandering trails that stretch throughout an expansive and verdant green garden bordered by raspberry bushes.  Thick vegetation grows at the edges of the plot, while a rickety scarecrow stands guard over a wide field of pale flax.  Several varieties of squash are clustered around tidy rows of carrots, tomatoes, pea pods, strawberries, lettuce and cabbage.  A sturdy workbench rests beneath a tool rack holding a number of burlap sacks and stained shovels."
    ],
